Szubsk-Towarzystwo  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Krośniewice, within Kutno County, Łódź Voivodeship, in central Poland. It lies approximately  south-east of Krośniewice,  west of Kutno, and  north of the regional capital Łódź.
